metadata.name: No. Halo Irene 1950
metadata.description:
I've been having this idea of an oil acrylic painting, using abstract expressionism that bleeds color into the frame. "Irene" is my mother's middle name. She was born in "1950." The "Halo" stands for her spirit, watching over me since she passed. 

Oil Acrylic on Canvas 16x20 

NFT includes physical: Framed 18x22 
Oil Acrylic Colour by Winsor and Newton
